              10' x 20' area.
    %br/ 
    %br/ 
    %p.light-gray.width-80.align-center
      %span.heavy-font 
        Can't decide what's best?
        %span.dark-blue Don't worry!
      %br/ 
      We'll always give you
      the best price
      based on your storage needs.
    .blue-bar.hide-on-small.half-opacity
    %br/ 
    %br/ 
    .container.row.pricing-wrapper
      %h3.dark-gray.no-margin
        Lowest Price
        %span.blue Guarantee!
      %hr.width-80.half-opacity
      %br/ 
      .row
        .col-md-2.col-md-offset-1
          %img{:src => "https://s3.amazonaws.com/storage_rails_app_dev/images/best-price.png", :alt => ""}/ 
        .col-md-8
          %p.align-left
            Already use storage? We offer a  
            %span.heavy-font.blue  minimum of 15% savings
            above your current price gauranteed! Plus, our free pickups make switching easy.
            %br/ 
            %br/ 
            Call us at 720-583-5826 to get started!
      %br/
      %br/ 
      .double-line.half-opacity.width-80.center-margin
